---
import "../styles/global.css";
import BasePageLayout from "../layouts/BasePageLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "About Me";

---

<BasePageLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h2>About Me</h2>    
  <div class="content">
      <p>
        When young me went to the doctor, my mom told me:
      </p>
      <p> 
        "You should learn to make and design stuff like those tools the doctor uses!"
      </p>
      
    <p>
      Well, nearly a decade and a half later and still interested in all things tech...

      <br>
      I can comfortably say, hardware or software; give me some time and I can hold to that thought my momma had.
    </p>

    I don't know what the future holds, but I'm willing to see it with you, reader.
    <br>
    Still need to add more, so be on the lookout.
    
    
  </div>
</BasePageLayout>
